African swine fever [ASF], Laos
-------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 20 Jun 2019 from Dr. Somphanh Chanphengxay, Director General, Department of Livestock and Fisheries, Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry, Vientiane, Laos

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 2 Jun 2019
Date of confirmation of the event: 17 Jun 2019
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease in the country
Causal agent: African swine fever virus
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks: 7
Outbreak 1 (ASF-2019-01): Samakkhixay, Toumlan, Saravane
Date of start of the outbreak: 2 Jun 2019
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
